				<span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span lang="fr">
				<font face="Arial"><span style="background-color: #EEECE1">Note</span>: 
				The nature of the 'Communion event', i.e., one wherein two 
				actors are engaged in distinct actions guided by different laws, 
				does not always allow for sharp demarcations in <i>discussions</i> 
				of the Canon 915 and 916. </font></span></span></p>
