		<a target="_blank" href="https://canonlawblog.wordpress.com/2007/09/10/abp-raymond-burke-on-canon-915/" style="text-decoration: none">
		here</a>.</font></span></span><font face="Arial"> </font>
		<span class="z3988"
		span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-family: Arial">
		&#9642; </span>
		<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Burke’s 
		article on Canon 915 now available in <i>Periodica</i>. &gt; Decretal canon 
		law. CCEO. 1917 Code.</span></p>
		<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
		&nbsp;</p>
		<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
		&nbsp;</p>
		<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
		<font face="Arial">&nbsp;• Peters' Blog,</font><span class="z3988"><span style="letter-spacing: normal"><font face="Arial"> 
		</font></span></span><font face="Arial">09 apr 2007,
		<a target="_blank" href="https://canonlawblog.wordpress.com/2007/04/09/denial-of-communion-to-a-lesbian-couple/" style="text-decoration: none">
		here</a>. </font>
		<span class="z3988"
		span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-family: Arial">
		&#9642; A lesbian couple who proclaims their activity is rightly denied 
		hcc. &gt; Canon 915. Ricken. Miller. Raske.</span></p>
